Package: PristineSeasR2
Title: Tools for Pristine Seas Scientific Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan", "Mayorga", , "marine.data.science@ngs.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions for analyzing Pristine Seas scientific data,
    custom color palettes and themes for data visualization, and standardized
    vocabularies for consistent data analysis across expeditions. 
    Designed for internal use by Pristine Seas research team to enhance workflow efficiency 
    and maintain analytical consistency.
